                     <interp inst="t18180909-298-person2069" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             DURHAM. I am a pawnbroker, and live in Holywell-lane. On the 6th of August the prisoner pledged three pieces of carpet with me he afterwards redeemed them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-298-person2070">
                  SAMUEL 
                  JAMES
               <interp inst="t18180909-298-person2070" type="surname" value="JAMES"></interp>
