                     <interp inst="t18180909-298-person2070" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             WOOLLAT. I am a pawnbroker, and live in Oxford-street. On the 6th of August the prisoner sold<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181809090094"></xptr>me the painting of a chesnut cart-horse for 6s. - I sold it again.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I understood I was to fetch them. I afterwards got drunk and sold them.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18180909-298-verdict1641" type="verdictDescription">
